layers.name: ðŸ“± HoloVault/Profile/New Profile no Existing Personas

Your personal information is managed by you in 1 location, 'HoloVault'. Other applications ask to borrow your info for a set amount of time and you can revoke that access when ever you like. Also you don't have to keep filling out the same info for every app and giving away your info. 'HoloVault' helps you reuse info you've already saved.
